msgstr "ຕິດຕໍ່ພວກເຮົາ"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_pricelist_boxed
msgid "Crayons and Markers Set"
msgstr "ຊຸດສໍສີ ແລະ ສໍເມຈິກ"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_split_intro
msgid "Create an environment<br/>for growth"
msgstr "ສ້າງສະພາບແວດລ້ອມ<br/>ເພື່ອການເຕີບໃຫຍ່"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_unveil
msgid ""
"Create joyful memories and foster growth in a loving, playful environment."
msgstr ""
"ສ້າງຄວາມຊົງຈຳທີ່ມ່ວນຊື່ນ ແລະ ສົ່ງເສີມການເຕີບໃຫຍ່ໃນສະພາບແວດລ້ອມທີ່ເຕັມໄປດ້ວຍຄວາມຮັກ ແລະ ການຫຼິ້ນ."

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_wavy_grid
msgid "Creative Play"
msgstr "ການຫຼິ້ນຢ່າງສ້າງສັນ"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_images_mosaic
msgid "Discover fun and engaging activities designed for young learners."
msgstr "ຄົ້ນພົບກິດຈະກຳທີ່ມ່ວນຊື່ນ ແລະ ໜ້າສົນໃຈ ທີ່ອອກແບບມາສຳລັບຜູ້ຮຽນໂຕນ້ອຍ."

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_carousel_intro
msgid "Discover joyful learning"
msgstr "ຄົ້ນພົບການຮຽນຮູ້ທີ່ເຕັມໄປດ້ວຍຄວາມສຸກ"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_cta_box
msgid "Discover our wide range of destinations for children holidays<br/><br/>"
msgstr "ຄົ້ນພົບຈຸດໝາຍປາຍທາງທີ່ຫຼາກຫຼາຍສຳລັບວັນຢຸດພັກຜ່ອນຂອງເດັກນ້ອຍ<br/><br/>"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_intro_pill
