msgstr "ຄົ້ນພົບ<br/>ໂລກໃບນ້ອຍຂອງພວກເຮົາ"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_text_cover
msgid "Discover<br/>our nursery"
msgstr "ຄົ້ນພົບ<br/>ໂຮງລ້ຽງເດັກຂອງພວກເຮົາ"

